sj = StringJoiner(prefix='[', suffix=']')
sj.add_multi(1, 2, 3, 'e4')
self.assertEqual('[1,2,3,e4]', str(sj))
expected__repr__ = (
    '{"separator": ",", "prefix": "[", "suffix": "]", "nelem": 4, "str_length": 10, "elements": ["1", "2", "3", "e4"]}'
    )
self.assertEqual(expected__repr__, repr(sj))
